message.body: Hey! You guys opening or going on later tonight? -candra
Music ends at 11. Hmm. Maybe we play sometime after nine....you will be on the guest list if there is one:)
Aw gee whiz, thx!
And if y'all need anything (place to stay, foods, laundry doins, etc) just let me know!
A floor to sleep on would be most excellent! We are in town now headed for the venue.
Sweet! 4 of you right? Our place is pretty small so we might have to find a spot for one or two of you, I'll see what I can do. Or y'all gonna hafta get ruhl cozy...
Yeah!
This may be interesting... Apparently our booking agent set up this Philly show with the bar owner, who in turn forgot to tell the promoter. Maybe we have a gig....?
Oh no!!
If it falls through, come kidnap me
Cool
Yes yes! Just keep me posted. I'ma swing by real soon, I'm only a few blocks away at a friends thing right now
Nope! But awesome! What's the address?
We picked up a venue. Lickety split. Heard of it?
401 south street
No cover me thinks. We go on way later. Maybe 12, but come hang when you want
Nice
Cool, I'll be there in about half an hour
Ok
On our way
Knock knock
